body:
can you move this up and make it (right now we unnecessarily call `bernoulli_` when `p == 1`)
```python
if self.p == 1:
    self.noise.fill_(0)
else:
    self.noise.bernoulli_(1 - self.p)
    if self.scale_train:
        self.noise.div_(1 - self.p)
```

